#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "The requested documentation was not found on your computer."
msgstr "Zahtevane dokumentacije ni bilo najdene na vašem računalniku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:27
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The documentation may not exist, or it may not have been installed with the "
"application."
msgstr "Dokumentacija ne obstaja ali pa ni bila nameščena z aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:30
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please do not email the author of this page to find the missing document. He "
"will just tell you to follow the instructions on this page."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, ne pošiljajte e-pošte avtorju te strani za manjkajoči dokument. "
"Svetoval vam bo, da sledite navodilom na tej strani."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to solve this issue"
msgstr "Kako rešiti to težavo"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the application is &kde; software, first use the search function in "
"&khelpcenter;. In some cases, the documentation has a different name than "
"the software was using to try to find it. If that doesn't work, try "
"searching the <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Documentation site</"
"ulink> for the requested documentation. If you find the documentation on "
"that site, your distribution might ship a separate package for documentation "
"(&eg; called plasma-doc for documentation related to &plasma;). Please use "
"the package manager of your distribution to find and install the missing "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Če je aplikacija programska oprema &kde; najprej uporabite funkcijo iskanja "
"v &khelpcenter;. V nekaterih primerih ima dokumentacija drugačno ime od "
"tega, ki ga je programska oprema uporabljala za iskanje. Če to ne deluje, "
"poskusite poiskati <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; Spletno mesto "
"z dokumentacijo</ulink> za zahtevano dokumentacijo. Če najdete dokumentacijo "
"na tem mestu, bo vaša distribucija morda poslala ločen paket za "
"dokumentacijo (&eg; imenovan plasma-doc za dokumentacijo, povezano s "
"&plasma;). Za iskanje in namestitev manjkajoče dokumentacije uporabite "
"upravljalnik paketov vaše distribucije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use a source based distribution, such as Gentoo, be sure that there "
"are not any configuration settings (USE flags in Gentoo) that might have "
"disabled the installation of the documentation."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate distribucijo, ki temelji na viru, kot je npr. Gentoo, se "
"prepričajte, da ni konfiguracijskih nastavitev (zastavice USE v Gentoo), ki "
"bi lahko onemogočile namestitev dokumentacije."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have done that, but still get this page displayed instead of the "
"application handbook, you probably found a bug in the help system. In this "
"case, please report this on the <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde;'s "
"bugtracker</ulink> under the KIO product."
msgstr ""
"Če ste to storili, vendar vam namesto priročnika za aplikacijo še vedno "
"prikazuje to stran, ste verjetno našli napako v sistemu pomoči. V tem "
"primeru prosimo, da to prijavite na <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/"
"\">&kde;-jev sledilnik hroščev</ulink> pod izdelkom KIO."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you do not find any documentation on the <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde."
"org/\">&kde; Documentation site</ulink>, the application may not have "
"offline documentation. Please report this on the <ulink url=\"https://bugs."
"kde.org/\">&kde;'s bugtracker</ulink> under the product for the application."
msgstr ""
"Če ne najdete nobene dokumentacije na <ulink url=\"https://docs.kde.org/"
"\">&kde; Spletnem mestu z dokumentacijo</ulink>, aplikacija morda nima "
"dokumentacije, dostopne brez povezave. Prosimo, da to prijavite na <ulink "
"url=\"https://bugs.kde.org/\">&kde;-jev sledilnik horščev</ulink> pod "
"izdelkom za aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case the application does not have offline documentation, you should use "
"the online resources <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/\">UserBase "
"Documentation</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde; "
"Community Forums</ulink> to get help."
msgstr ""
"V primeru, da aplikacija nima dokumentacije brez povezave, uporabite spletne "
"vire <ulink url=\"https://userbase.kde.org/\">UserBase Dokumentacijo</ulink> "
"in <ulink url=\"https://forum.kde.org/\">&kde;-jevi  Forumi Skupnosti</"
"ulink> za pomoč."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For non-&kde; applications, please contact the application author to "
"determine whether there should be offline documentation available."
msgstr ""
"Za aplikacije, ki niso &kde;, prosimo kontaktirajte avtorja aplikacije, da "
"vam pove, če naj bi obstajala dokumentacija brez povezave."
